{
  "stem": "26983.11",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they couldn't have their eyes everywhere, and because it was mixed with civil population, somehow we got some food into our wagon, which surely saved us, because the journey continued quite a long time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember we passed Prague.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were somewhere in a railway station near Prague.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went further on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the way, one SS let us once out to make toilet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before, what we could do is when-- I mean, I told you we had this melted snow, and we took our blankets and we made little square pieces like a handkerchief and as long as there was something left of the blankets, we went on the toilet on these blankets and we throw it out.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But later, even this we couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After quite a long time, it was about I guess a week or maybe longer, we arrived at Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know that it's Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we arrived in Austria, and I still mostly had some aesthetical something in me and I looked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was completely different from Auschwitz, because there were mountains and the buildings were from stones.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know in Mauthausen, they have quarries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everything was made from stone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was completely different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the looks from Birkenau--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the surrounding was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a sunny day and blue skies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we arrived--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the end of January.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess around the 25 of January, something like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had to walk quite a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw again the prisoners and we came to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, there was some very, for us, old prisoner, meaning there many years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some were even 12 years since '39, political prisoners and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
